<h1 align="center">
  Gatsby-Blog
</h1>

## :rocket: Quick start.

■ Gatsby.jsのプロジェクト作成.
```shell
gatsby new gatsby-blog https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby-starter-blog
cd gatsby-blog/
gatsby develop
gatsby clean
```

■ githubに追加.
```shell
git init
git add .
git commit -m "Initial Commit"
git remote add origin https://github.com/machio77777/gatsby-blog.git
git push -u origin master
```
